{"tid":747128,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日媒：異世界穿越作品追捧者多是大叔","createTime":"2018-07-18T06:36:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-19T01:11:40.000Z","uid":184679,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b94cb710ab75ab70167015a092ef4acfdd6a4092","tid":747128,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T06:36:25.000Z","msg":"幾乎每一季度的新番動畫都會出現異世界穿越題材的作品，而推崇這些作品的人居然多是三四十歲的大叔？這個結論被刊登在報紙上後，網友們對此展開討論。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/3/2018/07/14/f/f0b533aec2765e592b7be0ef9f02135b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F3%2F2018%2F07%2F14%2Ff%2Ff0b533aec2765e592b7be0ef9f02135b.jpg&h=09c4c497&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年6月，日本經濟新聞報紙刊登了一篇報導，內容分析異世界作品的主要粉絲是30到40歲的大叔，原因是他們都由於人生不如意而夢想著能夠&ldquo;重來一次&rdquo;，並且穿越之後可以實現各種遙不可及的願望。然而從報紙發行之後到現在的一個多月時間里，許多日本網友依然對此爭論不休，有人認為這種作品更受未成年人喜愛，也有人覺得報紙說得沒錯，逃避現實是必須的。<br />\n<br />\n日本經濟新聞的這篇報導指出異世界和穿越類輕小說靠著30到40歲的大叔的廣泛支持而超越了傳統的校園題材，因為許多劇中主角都是在現實失意，卻在異世界大顯身手闖出一片天，非常符合大叔們想要人生&ldquo;重來一次&rdquo;的願望。比如上個季度播出的《爆肝工程師的異世界狂想曲》里，男主角原本是一名整天忙於工作的社畜，穿越到異世界後瞬間就成了超強冒險者，並且受到各種美少女的追捧。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/3/2018/07/14/d/d2c330f2d2b9b20fba28b9b8c2328af2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F3%2F2018%2F07%2F14%2Fd%2Fd2c330f2d2b9b20fba28b9b8c2328af2.jpg&h=48e46b80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然原作者們並未指出這種作品更加適合哪個年齡層的讀者，但不少日本網友卻為了這篇報導爭論了一個多月時間，很多人都覺得既然是動漫題材，那麼這種異世界作品應該比較受未成年人歡迎才對，主要的粉絲怎麼可能是大叔呢？不過也有人覺得大叔的確需要逃避現實的渠道，閱讀這種爽快的內容更能讓人放鬆。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/3/2018/07/14/5/555a927b7bfa10fafee57cbe2296a07a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F3%2F2018%2F07%2F14%2F5%2F555a927b7bfa10fafee57cbe2296a07a.jpg&h=735f72a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&ldquo;人生失敗組真的會想要去異世界開無雙嗎？&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/3/2018/07/14/1/10d4069f47d720c5205ffb1d17bfc0dc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F3%2F2018%2F07%2F14%2F1%2F10d4069f47d720c5205ffb1d17bfc0dc.jpg&h=50996a71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&ldquo;應該有阿宅管理層人士會想要逃避現實吧&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/3/2018/07/14/7/7c1dba626903e73a593126b61dee145c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F3%2F2018%2F07%2F14%2F7%2F7c1dba626903e73a593126b61dee145c.jpg&h=78640039&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&ldquo;可以理解有人只寫得出這種作品，但卻很難理解只讀這種作品的人&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/3/2018/07/14/8/832fd530eb6f5a947b71b69aeaaddcec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F3%2F2018%2F07%2F14%2F8%2F832fd530eb6f5a947b71b69aeaaddcec.jpg&h=c3f67b48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&ldquo;這種人就是碰過很多挫折卻無法跨越吧？最後只能看這種逃避現實的作品&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/3/2018/07/14/0/055afeb8144b3ea547ea85ed49959e8e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F3%2F2018%2F07%2F14%2F0%2F055afeb8144b3ea547ea85ed49959e8e.jpg&h=9dd4a5c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&ldquo;人們不都是喜歡三國誌或幕末誌士那種英雄故事嗎？&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/3/2018/07/14/e/e76882f5268dbae356c8a388c1547614.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F3%2F2018%2F07%2F14%2Fe%2Fe76882f5268dbae356c8a388c1547614.jpg&h=b72cb2f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&ldquo;大叔才不會喜歡看男主角從失敗中成長的故事啦&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n從客觀條件考慮，如果倒退十幾年的話這些所謂的&ldquo;大叔&rdquo;也是追新番看輕小說的年輕人，這樣一來年齡跨度就顯得比較合理了。再加上平時工作的壓力，誠如網友所言，這些被工作支配生活的大叔確實需要一定程度上的&ldquo;逃避現實&rdquo;，而看異世界穿越題材作品則是最為便利的方法&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sina.com.hk/news/article/20180714/0/5/2/%E6%97%A5%E5%AA%92-%E7%95%B0%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E7%A9%BF%E8%B6%8A%E4%BD%9C%E5%93%81%E7%B2%89%E7%B5%B2%E5%A4%9A%E6%98%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%8F%94-%E7%B6%B2%E5%8F%8B-%E9%80%83%E9%81%BF%E7%8F%BE%E5%AF%A6-9029989.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F20180714%2F0%2F5%2F2%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25AA%2592-%25E7%2595%25B0%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%2595%258C%25E7%25A9%25BF%25E8%25B6%258A%25E4%25BD%259C%25E5%2593%2581%25E7%25B2%2589%25E7%25B5%25B2%25E5%25A4%259A%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%258F%2594-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E5%258F%258B-%25E9%2580%2583%25E9%2581%25BF%25E7%258F%25BE%25E5%25AF%25A6-9029989.html&d=1TTr1zPgDAwmDBLIUtEFKAEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=bb0f09b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://sina.com.hk/news/article/20180714/0/5/2/%E6%97%A5%E5%AA%92-%E7%95%B0%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E7%A9%BF%E8%B6%8A%E4%BD%9C%E5%93%81%E7%B2%89%E7%B5%B2%E5%A4%9A%E6%98%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%8F%94-%E7%B6%B2%E5%8F%8B-%E9%80%83%E9%81%BF%E7%8F%BE%E5%AF%A6-9029989.html</a>"},{"pid":"8ec99e95fa1a59f7e9fc6502bd6162753364e898","tid":747128,"uid":52881,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T06:42:44.000Z","msg":"事實上呢個年紀多數都做緊高技術社畜/專業人士,FF下去另一個世界屈人機其實有咩問題"},{"pid":"f9e690c37b08bf75cf9cf59aff2f4f0fd030a2aa","tid":747128,"uid":30067,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T07:39:59.000Z","msg":"問題係 係現實係失敗者<br />\n去到異世界一樣會係失敗者<br />\n除非天生有特異功能"},{"pid":"ec4d7244be14e3b9114260e06089399082dd0373","tid":747128,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9e690c37b08bf75cf9cf59aff2f4f0fd030a2aa","tid":747128,"uid":30067,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T07:39:59.000Z","msg":"問題係 係現實係失敗者<br />\n去到異世界一樣會係失敗者<br />\n除非天生有特異功能"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T07:54:24.000Z","msg":"話明係異世界, 可能癲覆一切標準, 充滿中國特色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e2e5b653fe375391ceb0086843e15613a839c5c","tid":747128,"uid":53687,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f9e690c37b08bf75cf9cf59aff2f4f0fd030a2aa","tid":747128,"uid":30067,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T07:39:59.000Z","msg":"問題係 係現實係失敗者<br />\n去到異世界一樣會係失敗者<br />\n除非天生有特異功能"},"c